{"id":517237,"date":[{"year":1972,"month":4,"day":2}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"","genre":"","count":"248","ytitle":"","mtitle":"友谊的歌","ftitle":"","authors":["邱荣其"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上港三区　邱荣其"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卸麦种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暖风吹开了浪花千层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗欢笑着迎接亲人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山鹰之国运来了麦种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"码头上一片欢腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千包万袋不觉重呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱挥舞双臂要学那展翅的“山鹰”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一粒良种不能丢呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级的委托记在心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚锣鼓传喜讯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽笛高歌货卸尽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮欢送提前启航的外轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满载着国际主义友情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装钢轨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝布围巾——腰里扎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五尺银翘——手中拿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝令吊钩上下舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安排钢轨躺仓下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜看水手把锚拔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮送船走天涯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢轨运往坦桑尼亚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情厚谊传遍亚非拉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海港工人的红心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着赤道战鼓在跳动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲觉醒的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛开香飘万里的友谊花"}]}